Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.05,Flashback,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you.{long}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.40,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,Back then, I made a promise to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.12,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,A very important promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if your fever is gone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My temperature is the same as yours, so that means it’s gone!{FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m going to go deliver newspapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, don’t go out there.{you can’t}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you went on your newspaper run during rainy days, your cold got even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry! It’s all about mind over matter!{病は気から 【やまいはきから】 (exp) sickness and health start with the mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you should really stay in bed!{blarg}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom went to heaven the year Asu was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad disappeared after accumulating gambling debts.{usage of "accumulate" in this sentence is still somewhat lulzy}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, we were abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a 40-year-old, one-room,\Ndilapidated apartment with no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, the congee is done!{粥 【かゆ】 (n) thin rice porridge; watery cooked rice; rice gruel;}{congee but eh}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s still hot, so be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ve still got an appetite\Nso I’m sure you’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asu, aren’t you going to eat?{direct address before or after OH THE HUMANITY}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I’m not hungry yet.{I don’t feel like eating now…}{OMG MOAR FORESHADOWING}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You’ve been sweating, so I’ll have to wash you down and dry you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It’s hot.{THIS SCENE IS HOT UNF}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that okay? Do you need more ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it’s fine, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you get lots of rest, I’m sure you’ll get better in no time.{I know that I’ll feel a whole lot better if we can just curb that temperature of yours a little.}{Just rest up while I take your temperature periodically and you’ll be fine.}
