Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.39,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,No, no! I have to hurry up and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.37,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I can’t continue making Asu worry like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! I’ve made a complete recover{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}.{全快 【ぜんかい】 (n,vs) complete recovery of health}
