Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.78,Flashback,,0,0,0,,He{\fsp-1}y{\fsp}, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.04,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Why do you smile whenever you see dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}You see, it’s because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,You see, it’s because the dandelions look so happy and carefree to me.
