Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}Yes.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.88,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}That’s why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,That’s why they remind me of you, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Me?
