Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.41,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Just like the dandelions, you always seem to be smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}That’s why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,That’s why I smile whenever I see dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\3c&HFFFFFF&}Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That’s right. Mom wasn’t smiling because she was looking at the dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.{"face" is a more accurate translation but I really like this phrasing better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\t(338,1339,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\4a&HFF&)}Mom was…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I never smiled for Asu.
