Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.49,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:46.71,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,The thing that only I can do for Asu. The most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.00,Dialogue-italic,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten!
